raw_text = "~ talk
{{green}}: {{blue}}? Is that you?
{{teardrop_blue}}: Do not rip. Do not tear. Inside is where it should go...
{{green}}: [#expression=sorry] No, don't think like that. This isn't meditation.
{{ouroboros}}: [#font=above] Nom, {{observer}} does not see the real {{blue}}.
{{green}}: [#expression=scared] So this is an illusion too?
{{green}}: [#expression=sorry] Does that mean this is how we imagine {{blue}} to be like on the inside, but it's not really how {{blue}} really feels?
{{ouroboros}}: Nom, the {{observer}} has not seen the real {{blue}}. Only a {{reflection}}.
{{green}}: [#expression=scared] Then, the {{blue}} who I mentored all this time was an illusion too.
{{ouroboros}}: When the {{observer}} reveals a {{reflection}}, [color=yellow] the {{observer}}'s {{real}} space will collapse. [/color]
{{green}}: [#expression=scared] Then... everything I know is...
{{green}}: [#expression=sorry] I understand now. That's why Magiscience never made any sense.
{{ouroboros}}: Nom, 
=> END!"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.10.1"
